Hitilafu ya ndani ya seva imetokea
translations.This file is too big to be opened. Pleas: Faili hii ni kubwa sana kufunguliwa. Tafadhali pakua faili badala yake.
translations.The file you are working on was updated: Faili unayofanyia kazi ilisasishwa kwa sasa.
translations.You don't have enough permission to crea: Huna ruhusa ya kutosha kuunda faili
translations.Draw.io app not configured! Please conta: Programu ya Draw.io haijasanidiwa! Tafadhali wasiliana na msimamizi.
translations.Integrates draw.io diagrams editor with: Huunganisha kihariri cha michoro ya draw.io na Nextcloud
Hitilafu: Utengenezaji wa faili jipya umeshindikana
translations.Note: To enable realtime collaboration,: Kumbuka: Ili kuwezesha ushirikiano wa wakati halisi, acha bila kitu au uweke (https://embed.diagrams.net)
translations.Activate offline mode in Draw.io?: Ungependa kuwasha hali ya nje ya mtandao katika Draw.io?
translations.When the \"offline mode\" is active, thi: Wakati "hali ya nje ya mtandao" inatumika, hii huzima utendakazi na vipengele vyote vya mbali ili kulinda faragha ya watumiaji. Draw.io pia itakuwa katika Kiingereza pekee, hata kama utaweka lugha tofauti wewe mwenyewe.
translations.Note: To enable realtime collaboration,: Kumbuka: Ili kuwezesha ushirikiano wa wakati halisi, uhifadhi otomatiki lazima uwe amilifu.
translations.Enable diagram previews?: Ungependa kuwasha onyesho la kukagua mchoro?
translations.Note: Disable previews to save storage s: Kumbuka: Zima onyesho la kukagua ili kuhifadhi nafasi ya kuhifadhi inayotumika kuhifadhi picha za onyesho la kukagua mchoro
